high_descs: Leave the bedroom, take a right and turn around on the countertop in the kitchen.
Take the spatula from the kitchen counter top.
Turn right and move towards the sink.
Open the tap to wash the spatula.
Take away the spatula and keep it aside the sink.
anns.task_desc: Take the Spatula in the kitchen and wash it in the sink to use.

high_descs: Exit from the bedroom turn right walk back go to the countertop in the kitchen.
See the stainless steel sink, turn right on the along turn left.
Take the spatula from the sink.
anns.task_desc: Take the spatula to the sink for cleaning.

high_descs: In bedroom head towards the door then turn right to countertop
Take the spatula from the counter top.
Turn around and go near to the sink.
Put the spatula in the sink, pour the water and take it back.
Place the spatula near to the sink.
anns.task_desc: Take the spatula from the counter top, clean it, and place it near to the sink.
